  <title>How to change the game board size</title>

  <p>You can select a field size at the start of the application.</p>

  <p>Select one of the grid sizes:</p>
  <list>
    <item><p>a 8 × 8 board with 10 mines</p></item>
    <item><p>a 16 × 16 board with 40 mines</p></item>
    <item><p>a 30 × 16 board with 99 mines</p></item>
    <item><p>a custom board, where you chose the size and the number of
    mines</p></item>
  </list>

  <p>To change the <link xref="board-size">board size</link> later, press the
  <gui style="button">Change Difficulty</gui> button on the right.</p>

